name: 3.VESSEL - They Do knock
description:
They do knock, and have to announce themselves.

I've spend almost all night on it, listening to :

--> Gonjasufi - Callus, MU.ZZ.LE
--> Paavoharju - all discography
--> Coil - "careful what you wish for"
--> Leya - Flood Dream


All those are really full of angst, elegy or/and melancolia, so is the mouth to open the lock.

Black ink on black ink on black ink on white paper.
